abstract: |-
  deploy2zenodo is a shell script to deploy your data to
  zenodo. You can use it in a CI pipeline as an automatic
  workflow.

  Environmental variables allow very flexible use. Depending
  on the selected flags, the data can be curated before
  deployment in a merge request, in the zenodo web interface
  or not curated at all.
